This is a fork of Discord Data Package Explorer
(https://github.com/Androz2091/discord-data-package-explorer) by
Androz2091. It was modified starting in 2026 (by 2cuteflakes) to run
locally instead of relying on a hosted instance or third-party
identity-lookup APIs, with additional features added on top - see the
project's git history for the full list of changes.
